92&nbsp;Undina]] || [[:Category:Veritas asteroids|cat]] || {{LoMP|490|list}}\n|-id=610\n| 610 || [[Karin family]] || KAR || align=center | 541 || align=center | outer || align=center | [[S-type asteroid|S]] || 0.21 || [[832 Karin]]. Recently formed family located within the [[#605|Koronis family]].<ref name=\"Nesvorny-2014\" />{{rp|8,18}} || [[:Category:Karin asteroids|cat]] || {{LoMP|832|list}}\n|-id=611\n| 611 || Na\u00ebma family || NAE || align=center | 301 || align=center | outer || align=center | [[C-type asteroid|C]] || 0.08 || [[845 Na\u00ebma]], adj. Na\u00ebmian || [[:Category:Na\u00ebma asteroids|cat]] || {{LoMP|845|list}}\n|-id=612\n| 612 || Tirela family<br />{{small|(Klumpkea family)}} || TIR || align=center | 1395 || align=center | outer || align=center | [[S-type asteroid|S]] || 0.07 || [[1400 Tirela]], alternatively named after [[1040&nbsp;Klumpkea]] (AstDyS) || [[:Category:Tirela asteroids|cat]] || {{LoMP|1400|list}}\n|-id=613\n| 613 || Lixiaohua family<br />{{small|(Gantrisch family)}} || LIX || align=center | 756 || align=center | outer || align=center | CX || 0.04 || [[3556 Lixiaohua]]; although member [[3330&nbsp;Gantrisch]] is both larger and lower numbered ([http://zoran.aob.rs/lixiaohua.pdf src)]  || [[:Category:Lixiaohua asteroids|cat]] || {{LoMP|3556|list}}\n|-id=614\n| 614 || Telramund family<br />{{small|(Klytaemnestra family)}} || TEL || align=center | 468 || align=center | outer || align=center | [[S-type asteroid|S]] || 0.22 || [[9506 Telramund]]; alternatively named after [[179&nbsp;Klytaemnestra]] by [[Joseph Masiero|Masiero]] and by [[Andrea Milani (mathematician)|Milani]] || [[:Category:Telramund asteroids|cat]] || {{LoMP|9506|list}}\n|-id=615\n| 615 || ''unnamed family'' || 615 || align=center | 104 || align=center | outer || align=center | CX || 0.17 || {{mpl|(18405) 1993 FY|12}} || \u2014 || {{LoMP|18405|list}}\n|-id=616\n| 616 || Charis family || CHA || align=center | 808 || align=center | outer || align=center | [[C-type aste